text:
You're about to see a map of campus with trivia questions and locations. Once you've reached a location that has a [?] symbol it will turn into a blue button you can press. Once you have completed the location it will turn gold.

This website will not store information about you or your location. Your phone will use your location to work out where you are on our map.

Please only use this app during the day time.

Have fun!
This is the start of a new experiment.
